narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learnt a lot about Native Americans and indigenous lifeways.
Beautiful texts and thoughtful discussions. Loved being a part of it.

narratives.question_text: How well did the knowledge, skills, and insights gained in this class align with your expectations?
comments: Directly in line with my expectations - explanations were set up well.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of the course and how could it be improved?
comments: Too many generalizations were made, and I often felt misunderstood in class discussions Student discussion questions often felt irrelevant or completely disconnected from the readings

narratives.question_text: What advice would you give to a student considering taking this class?
comments: Students who want to know something about indigenous ways of thinking, Native Americans and even interdependence between man and nature should take this course.
